@startuml

title BeastLocker E-commerce Platform - User Flow Diagram
header Internship Project | Academic Year 2025-2026
footer Page 1/1

[*] --> Homepage

state Homepage
state ProductListing
state ProductDetail
state Checkout
state OrderConfirmation

Homepage --> ProductListing : Browse Category\n(header menu)
Homepage --> ProductListing : Search Product\n(filters listing)
Homepage --> ProductDetail : Click Featured Product

ProductListing --> ProductListing : Search/Filter/Sort
ProductListing --> ProductDetail : Select Product
ProductListing --> Checkout : Quick Add to Cart
ProductListing --> Homepage : Return Home

ProductDetail --> ProductDetail : View Recommended Product
ProductDetail --> Checkout : Add to Cart
ProductDetail --> ProductListing : Back to Listing
ProductDetail --> Homepage : Return Home

Checkout --> OrderConfirmation : Complete Order
Checkout --> ProductListing : Continue Shopping

OrderConfirmation --> Homepage : Return Home
OrderConfirmation --> ProductListing : Browse More Products
OrderConfirmation --> [*] : Exit Site

note right of Homepage
  **Global Header (all pages):**
  • Logo → Home
  • Category Menu
  • Search Bar → filters Product Listing
  • Cart Icon → opens side panel
end note

note right of Checkout
  **Cart Side Panel:**
  • View cart items
  • Update quantities
  • Remove products
  • View subtotal
  • Proceed to Checkout
end note

@enduml